        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Special Activation\" aria-label=\"Special Activation\">*</span></p><p><em>The best gamble is one that secretly isn’t a gamble at all. Your insight sometimes reveals that seemingly random events are actually part of someone’s plan.</em></p><p>When you use your Opportunist, instead of rerolling the plot die, you can spend 2 focus to flip it to a specific result. If the die was showing <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" style=\"color: #98a4f5;\" data-tooltip=\"Opportunity\" aria-label=\"Opportunity\">O</span>, flip it to <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Always Active\" aria-label=\"Always Active\" style=\"color:rgb(173,19,19)\">c</span><span style=\"color:rgb(173,19,19)\">4</span>. If it was showing any <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Always Active\" aria-label=\"Always Active\" style=\"color:rgb(173,19,19)\">c</span>, flip it to <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" style=\"color: #98a4f5;\" data-tooltip=\"Opportunity\" aria-label=\"Opportunity\">O</span>.</p>",
